PrecisAuthority (a) to enter into Agreements which provide for the implementation of cooperative plans for the marketing of MAPLE SYRUP produced in 1990, with each of the following cooperative associations: 1. La coopérative des producteurs de sirop d'érable du Nouveau- Brunswick inc.; 2. La fédération des producteurs acéricoles; 3. Maple Syrup Producers Co-operative of Ontario Limited; and (b) for the appointment of the following professional accountants to inspect and audit the books and accounts of these associations: i) Auditors Services Unis de vérification et d'inspection inc.; ii) Maheux, Noiseux; iii) Barker, Stanley and Partners.
